query: SELECT o.id, o.status, o.totalSkus, o.processedSkus, o.totalCost, o.zipFileUrl, o.createdAt, o.completedAt, oi.sku, oi.status as itemStatus, oi.errorMessage FROM orders o LEFT JOIN order_items oi ON o.id = oi.orderId WHERE o.id >= 270000 ORDER BY o.id DESC LIMIT 10;
